<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Stargazeboutique – Ultimate Infographic</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin:20px; line-height:1.5; color:#222; }
h1,h2,h3 { margin:10px 0; }
.section { margin-bottom:25px; border-bottom:1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom:15px; }
.folder-tree { font-family: monospace; background:#f8f8f8; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; }
.workflow, .steps, .notes { margin:10px 0; padding:10px; background:#f0f8ff; border-radius:6px; }
.visual { display:inline-block; width:150px; margin:5px; text-align:center; vertical-align:top; }
.visual img { width:100%; height:100px; object-fit:cover; border:1px solid #ddd; }
.checklist li { margin:5px 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Stargazeboutique – Ultimate Infographic</h1>
<p><b>Version:</b> 2026.03 | <b>JS-Free, Professional, Tablet-Ready</b></p>

<!-- Section 1: Folder Structure -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Folder Structure</h2>
<pre class="folder-tree">
stargazeboutique/
├── index.html
├── shop.html
├── cart.html
├── wishlist.html
├── admin.html
├── category-pages/
├── images/
├── css/style.css
└── HTML-PDF-Template.html
</pre>
</div>

<!-- Section 2: Workflow -->
<div class="section workflow">
<h2>Product & Category Workflow</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Product:</b> Add → Edit → Delete → Refresh Browser</li>
<li><b>Category:</b> Add Section → Update & Add Products → Optional New Page</li>
<li><b>Cart & Wishlist:</b> Edit → Refresh → Verify Layout</li>
<li><b>Admin Panel:</b> Edit/Delete placeholders → Refresh</li>
<li><b>PDF Reference:</b> Insert Screenshots/Images → Print → Save as PDF</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- Section 3: Tablet Launch Steps -->
<div class="section steps">
<h2>Tablet Launch Steps</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
<li>Copy folder → tablet storage</li>
<li>Open <b>index.html</b> → verify homepage & banner</li>
<li>Navigate: Shop → Categories → Cart → Wishlist → Admin</li>
<li>Add/Edit/Delete products → Refresh Browser</li>
<li>Verify responsive layout (portrait & landscape)</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- Section 4: Visual Mockups -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Visual Mockups</h2>
<div class="visual">
<img src="images/product-images/kurti1.jpg" alt="Kurti 1">
<p>Kurti Set</p>
</div>
<div class="visual">
<img src="images/product-images/lehenga1.jpg" alt="Lehenga 1">
<p>Wedding Lehenga</p>
</div>
<div class="visual">
<img src="images/product-images/saree1.jpg" alt="Saree 1">
<p>Party Wear Saree</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Section 5: Notes & Best Practices -->
<div class="section notes">
<h2>Notes & Best Practices</h2>
<ul>
<li>Backup folder before editing</li>
<li>Compress images for faster tablet load</li>
<li>Unlimited products & categories</li>
<li>Fully JS-free, professional, responsive</li>
</ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
